description:
Amazing Facts broadcasts Bible-based programming 24/7 on the Amazing Facts TV (AFTV) satellite channel, broadcasting such programs as Amazing Facts Presents, Sabbath School Study Hour, and more featuring Pastor Doug Batchelor and other Spirit-led speakers. Start enjoying the best Christian network available, featuring ministries that deliver accurate, biblical, and inspirational information to grow your faith in the Lord.

Online
Watch AFTV at www.aftv.org, featuring live and on-demand programming.

Television
You can watch AFTV on the G19 satellite, which features dozens of other Christian channels, by visiting aftv.glorystar.tv to purchase an inexpensive satellite package capable of receiving AFTV or to get technical support. You can also call 866-406-7810.

You can also watch AFTV on any Roku streaming device. Visit Roku.com to learn more. Find us by searching for AFTV or Amazing Facts Television.
